---
title: Creamy Horseradish Chicken Linguine with Spinach
description: In this dish, lightly peppery horseradish pasta sauce is tempered by creaminess to deliver mind-blowing flavour. Fresh tarragon adds a touch of elegance and an unforgettable mild anise profile!
